'''麗莎·希頓'''（{{lang-en|'''Lisa Haydon'''}}，全名為：伊麗莎白·瑪麗·希頓，{{bd|1986年|6月17日|catIdx=H}}）是[[印度|印度]]女演員及模特兒。她最知名的電影作品是2014年的《女皇》（Queen），希頓的演出備受讚賞<ref>[http://www.filmfare.com/reviews/movie-review-queen-5546.html "Movie Review: Queen"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmfare.com/reviews/movie-review-queen-5546.html |date=20140310112517 }}. Filmfare. 7 March, 2014.</ref>。她亦是一名受過訓練的[[婆羅多舞|婆羅多舞]]舞者<ref>[http://ibnlive.in.com/photogallery/4831-8.html "Rascals: B'wood hottie Lisa Haydon in spicy item number"] {{Wayback|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/photogallery/4831-8.html |date=20140419020104 }}. CNN-IBN. Retrieved 18 April 2014.</ref>。

希頓的父親是印度人，母親則是澳洲及斯里蘭卡混血兒<ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Lisa-Haydon-wants-to-work-with-Hrithik/articleshow/6265852.cms?referral=PM "Lisa Haydon wants to work with Hrithik"] {{Wayback|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Lisa-Haydon-wants-to-work-with-Hrithik/articleshow/6265852.cms?referral=PM |date=20160204123044 }}. The Times of India. 7 August, 2010.</ref>。她曾在澳洲及[[美國|美國]]居住但在2007年搬回印度擔任模特兒<ref>[http://www.movies.com.pk/celebrity/Lisa-Haydon/5571/biography "Lisa Haydon Biography"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.movies.com.pk/celebrity/Lisa-Haydon/5571/biography |date=20140903215442 }}. CineBasti.com. Retrieved 22 May 2011.</ref>。

